item.title: CVE-2023-38026|2023-08-28T03:29:08.582Z -- spotcam%20co.%2C%20ltd. -- spotcam%20fhd%202
item.description: SpotCam Co., Ltd. SpotCam FHD 2 has a vulnerability of using hard-coded uBoot credentials. An remote attacker can exploit this vulnerability to access the system to perform arbitrary system operations or disrupt service.
